modules.description: Provides control sap.ushell.ui.shell.ShellAppTitle  This control is responsible to display the Shell Header Title. This control could be rendered in two different states: 1. Title only: only the title will be rendered inside the Shell Header 2. Title with popover button: A button will be placed in the Shell Header Title area. When the user clicks on the button, a popover will raise and render the innerControl as its content.  innerControl: the content of the popover. Will be destroyed by the ShellAppTitle control.
